      "message": "I don\u0027t know. \n\nGCE Emulation is in experimental stage yet (enabled only on a bunch of builders). There were reports it doesn\u0027t work with some version of gsutils. Need to investigate before enabling it everywhere.\n\nGit auth was explicitly disabled on CrOS bots some time ago. But looks like no more? Need to confirm is it enabled everywhere, then we can make it default.\n\nDocker: some recipes use \"docker login\" step. I don\u0027t know how it behaves when docker auth daemon is enabled.\n\nFirebase should be safe to enable everywhere. At worst it\u0027ll break few exotic recipes that use firebase in a weird way.",
